title: G-Shock X Complex - Elements of Style
description: G-SHOCK has braved the elements for 30 years. Its name is now synonymous with rugged durability, and G-SHOCK watches all possess a uniformity of toughness, but a wide variety of features and faces. From the devoted outdoorsman to the athlete-in-training to the urban warrior, G-SHOCK has something to offer for all walks of life. It's technology is complex, but its appeal is simple. G-SHOCK is elemental.
